Published parameter estimates from the literature

Source: R/param_estimates_published.R
param_estimates_published.Rd

Published estimates of epidemiological characteristics from both peer-reviewed and non-peer-reviewed resources, encoded by community members and approved by authors. For complete information on each estimate, see the actual dataset items.

param_estimates_published()

Source

  • https://github.com/midas-network/COVID-19/blob/master/parameter_estimates/2019_novel_coronavirus/estimates.csv

References

  • https://midasnetwork.us/covid-19/

See also
